{"tid":612402,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今天我不愛你了","createTime":"2018-03-31T20:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T23:12:17.000Z","uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61330e1bed113d50f8991779e022058f74d23dab","tid":612402,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信我吧"},{"pid":"cefd6b3d9795b47b16980e8f2d0afda18aad8df7","tid":612402,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:17:11.000Z","msg":"信"},{"pid":"bd4f7beb9147381893b9e652fa8a167ed38b296c","tid":612402,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cefd6b3d9795b47b16980e8f2d0afda18aad8df7","tid":612402,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:17:11.000Z","msg":"信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:19:40.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"a52d34e65d1980165a090534c9faeb6f593cdc48","tid":612402,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:22:49.000Z","msg":"嘻"},{"pid":"c4c518e1d07fa77e09879b58655bc292958966c6","tid":612402,"uid":97630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:29:40.000Z","msg":"愚人節快樂"},{"pid":"37502361fe71e05bbadd8422df26ba120a37a5bd","tid":612402,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c8cf8789fb14d8ce045a62d8fc1f46dd57c5193","tid":612402,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:45:59.000Z","msg":"今天睡不著不是因為太掛念你<br />\n我才不會記住你這個人呢<br />\n你一點都不可愛 一點都不美<br />\n我真的一點都不喜歡你<br />\n我這輩子最不喜歡你這個人了"},{"pid":"bbf0076f4d1ffe5e6dd623151f52b670fb7425ed","tid":612402,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:53:23.000Z","msg":"我馬上就會找到你<br />\n我會告訴你<br />\n我真的很愛你<br />\n你會笑著流淚<br />\n把雙手放在面上<br />\n和我剩下一個擁抱"},{"pid":"a69702fecd8d1e0078aa36e3bfb9b43856d56888","tid":612402,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:57:32.000Z","msg":"你會為我擔心<br />\n我會在意你的著緊<br />\n我會怕你擔心而不敢坦白<br />\n你會受傷 你會生氣<br />\n但你會回來<br />\n後來我會改變<br />\n但你也會改變<br />\n我會受傷 我會生氣<br />\n我亦會回來<br />\n然後我們都變了不少"},{"pid":"050279bfac2c84b36173fb3f5da1787e0e5a6fdd","tid":612402,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T21:03:32.000Z","msg":"今日是你生日<br />\n你穿白色的裙<br />\n坐了我的對面<br />\n等待我為你製造的驚喜<br />\n你只有開心 沒有驚喜<br />\n你早習慣了突發的事<br />\n過去你都會感動落淚<br />\n這次你沒有<br />\n因為你知道過去的已經過去<br />\n對面的是誰你沒有把他看清楚<br />\n你怕你不想過去"},{"pid":"40b45fb098fa510b54546ba206b50e4df456f999","tid":612402,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T22:20:47.000Z","msg":"明天再愛"},{"pid":"711e7475a0a7acd05731319112ac2a74d646a542","tid":612402,"uid":175733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T23:07:12.000Z","msg":"我會把你放下<br />\n不會再在乎你<br />\n因為不愛你了<br />\n不想你了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9522ad136c210e666375e931df2bfcbdcc46c1f","tid":612402,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T23:10:45.000Z","msg":"即使係愚人節 我都唔會開啲咁既玩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a81cd2c253c57593875c59360d1bbd0fe1ca891","tid":612402,"uid":153311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T23:12:17.000Z","msg":"會唔會玩得太大"}]}